{"article_id":"EFZlXLxwTj3JyIej","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US tariffs on $ 34bn","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"( £25.7bn )","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"of Chinese goods have come into effect ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"signalling the start of a trade war between the world 's two largest economies .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The 25 % levy came into effect at midnight Washington time .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"China has retaliated","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"by imposing a similar 25 % tariff on 545 US products ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"also worth a total of $ 34bn .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Beijing accused the US of starting the `` largest trade war in economic history '' .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"`` After the US activated its tariff measures against China ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"China 's measures against the US took effect immediately , ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"said Lu Kang , a foreign ministry spokesman .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Two companies in Shanghai told the BBC","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"that customs authorities were delaying clearance processes for US imports on Friday .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"The American tariffs are the result of President Donald Trump 's bid","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"to protect US jobs","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"and stop `` unfair transfers of American technology and intellectual property to China '' .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"The White House said","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"it would consult on tariffs on another $ 16bn of products ,","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"which","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Mr Trump has suggested","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"could come into effect later this month .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The imposition of the tariffs had little impact on Asian stock markets .","depth":3},{"id":23,"text":"The Shanghai Composite closed 0.5 % higher ,","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"but ended the week 3.5 % lower","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"- its seventh consecutive week of losses .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Tokyo closed 1.1 % higher ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"but Hong Kong fell 0.5 % in late trading .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Hikaru Sato at Daiwa Securities said","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"markets had already factored in the impact of the first round of tariffs .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Mr Trump has already imposed tariffs on imported washing machines and solar panels ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"and started charging levies on the imports of steel and aluminium from the European Union , Mexico and Canada .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"He has also threatened a 10 % levy on an additional $ 200bn of Chinese goods","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"if Beijng `` refuses to change its practices '' .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"The president upped the stakes on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"the amount of goods","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"subject to tariffs","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"could rise to more than $ 500bn .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"`` You have another 16","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"[ billion dollars ]","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"in two weeks ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and then ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"as you know ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"we have $ 200bn in abeyance","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and then after the $ 200bn , we have $ 300bn in abeyance .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"OK ?","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"So we have 50 plus 200 plus almost 300 , ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"The US tariffs","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"imposed so far","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"would affect the equivalent of 0.6 % of global trade","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"and account for 0.1 % of global GDP ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"according to Morgan Stanley in a research note","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"issued before Mr Trump 's comments on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Analysts are also concerned about the impact 